---
---

<section id="cartao" class="py-24 w-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary via-blue-600 to-blue-800 px-6 md:px-12 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-secondary rounded-full blur-3xl float-animation"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-10 w-80 h-80 bg-white rounded-full blur-3xl float-animation" style="animation-delay: 1.5s;"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-16 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center reveal-left">
      <span class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary uppercase tracking-[3px] mb-4">
        Cartão Fidelidade
      </span>
      
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
        Acumule pontos<br />e ganhe prêmios
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-blue-100 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Cadastre seu cartão fidelidade e comece a acumular pontos a cada compra. Troque por descontos e produtos exclusivos!
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <span class="text-3xl block mb-2">🎁</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Prêmios Exclusivos</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <span class="text-3xl block mb-2">💰</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Descontos Especiais</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <span class="text-3xl block mb-2">⭐</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Pontos a Cada Compra</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
          <span class="text-3xl block mb-2">📱</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-white font-medium">Acesso Fácil</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a 
        href="#contato" 
        class="btn-secondary inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base w-fit"
      >
        ✨ Cadastre-se Agora
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center reveal-right">
      <div class="w-full max-w-md aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-secondary glow float-animation">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556742049-0cfed4f6a45d?w=600&h=600&fit=crop" 
          alt="Cartão Fidelidade" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
